    <refname>SpacecraftHardware</refname>

    <refpurpose>Add hardware to a spacecraft</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>

    <para>The hardware fields allow you to attach pre-configured hardware
    models to a spacecraft. Current models include tank and thruster. Before
    you attach a hardware model to a spacecraft, you must first create the
    model.</para>

    <para><phrase role="ref_seealso">See Also</phrase>: <xref
    linkend="FuelTank"/>, <xref linkend="Thruster"/></para>
  </refsection>

